    "## 🗂️ Step 5 — Document Structuring (Tertiary LLM Fallback)\n",
    "\n",
    "Each page-chunk is sent to an LLM that returns a **structured JSON** of sections with:\n",
    "- `title`, `content`, `section_type`, `page_start`, `page_end`, `key_concepts`"
   ]
